summary: A Dwemer Player home \"Updates every week (Maybe)
descriptionHtml:
[color=#FF0000][size=3]Due to summer, the development of this mod is stopped.[/size][/color] 

[Center][img]http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-w1ELspvbm4c/T8ImuWKJ-_I/AAAAAAAAAJM/UXrR00LD0pk/s320/Saiwas.png[/img][/Center]


[color=#358CDC][size=2]WHAT DOES SAIWS MEAN?[/size][/color]

Saiws is a [i]gothic[/i] word for water.
I chose this name becouse i saw a underwater mod. [color=#FF0000][u](I don\'t remember what mod it was)[/u][/color]


[color=#358CDC][size=2]WHAT IS SAIWS?[/size][/color]

Saiws is a Dwemer player home in the middle of the sea.
Theres no way to go to Saiws, you have to row to Saiws. (The boat is realy a [i]door[/i])

[color=#358CDC][size=2]WHERE IS THE BOAT LOCATED?[/size][/color]

To get to Saiws go east of Dawnstar to get to the dock. (Map marker is shown)

[color=#358CDC][size=2]FEATURES TO COME[/size][/color]
More rooms
More clutter
Navmesh


[color=#358CDC][size=2]Compatibility issues[/size][/color]
Any mod that  modifies the cell [color=#FF0000]MarkarthVlindrelHall [/color] a lot.

[color=#358CDC][size=2]BUGS[/size][/color]
[color=#FF0000]Theres was a naming error in the mapping[/color]

[color=#358CDC][size=2]CONTACT/UPDATES[/size][/color]
To contact me contact me at Contact.stso@gmail.com

Updates at  [url=http://stso-stsodevelopment.blogspot.com/]This site[/url]
